{"tid":469612,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突然]渡邊麻友做雞照流出","createTime":"2017-11-15T13:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T08:57:33.000Z","uid":2169,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5300d8cb58e453fabeb10ec404352302d2e3cd","tid":469612,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"如圖，認真製作炸雞塊的麻友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/211138_b06e935695e4e4f6626ffd1bfab44ff0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F211138_b06e935695e4e4f6626ffd1bfab44ff0.jpg&h=2cc99534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據麻友自己說她很會做炸雞塊並且很好吃，那麼擅長做炸雞塊的麻友才沒有在手上寫小抄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/211219_3e636430425ab89c7be23c294cb73acd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F211219_3e636430425ab89c7be23c294cb73acd.jpg&h=419e58a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在秋葉原的akb咖啡廳里，我們的麻友選手所設計的菜單，也是滿滿炸雞塊！配上了用雞蛋做的木吃吃造型的炸雞塊飯！是不是感受到了麻友在設計菜單的用心了呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/211305_f91ac3ef437c175aa1d2638ff72792d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F211305_f91ac3ef437c175aa1d2638ff72792d3.jpg&h=ea01b130&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6da454daedf36050f15a95cc5b088af418b71ed9","tid":469612,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"@卡勞"},{"pid":"e5cf557906955b4b51d4edd9af6a16c8feba0a0c","tid":469612,"uid":88120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:20:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d13d8b18d81e8fa907795f7b6387539c7ca26a03","tid":469612,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/210116